                            <div class="col-md-8">
                                <h4>Team training</h4>
                                <div class="panel panel-purple margin-bottom-40">

                                    <table class="table table-striped">
                                        <thead>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th>Week</th>
                                                <th>Theme</th>
                                                <th>Description</th>
                                            </tr>
                                        </thead>
                                        <tbody>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>1</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Volleys and Smashes</td>
                                                <td>Sharpening up the technique at the net, specifically the grip, footwork and contact. How do these vary on low volleys and high volleys?</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>2</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>The Serving Team</td>
                                                <td>What is the role of the server? What types of serve are commonly used in doubles? And what is the role of their partner? How can he/she intercept effectively, looking specifically at the positioning, the timing, and the shot selection?</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>3</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>The Returning Team</td>
                                                <td>What options does the returner have in doubles? And what should he/she do next? Looking at neutralizing a good first serve effectively, as well as trying to gain the advantage from a weaker serve</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>4</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Groundstrokes</td>
                                                <td>Developing technique to achieve greater consistency from the back of the court, particular on crosscourt forehands and backhands. </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>5</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Moving as a Team (forwards/backwards)</td>
                                                <td>When and how should you approach the net together? Reading and responding to the situation. Where is the "threat" and how should you adjust your court positioning accordingly?</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>6</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Moving as a Team (lateral)</td>
                                                <td>How to cover the whole court effectively?</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>7</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Touch</td>
                                                <td>Developing the soft hands needed to play good "touch". Includes drop shots, drop volleys and short angles</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>8</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Serve and Volley</td>
                                                <td>How and when to serve and volley effectively, plus how to return effectively against the serve/volleyer</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>9</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Doubles Team Formations</td>
                                                <td>How and when to use the "I-Formation", the "Aussie Formation" and the both back situation, and how to return effectively against each. What type of serve works well, adn how can the serving team communicate this with each other? </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>10</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Match Practice - Doubles</td>
                                                <td>Playing points, while looking specifically at court positioning, shot selection and team work</td>
                                            </tr>
