                                    <table class="table table-striped">
                                        <thead>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th>Week</th>
                                                <th>Theme</th>
                                                <th>Description</th>
                                            </tr>
                                        </thead>
                                        <tbody>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>1</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Trading - forehands</td>
                                                <td>Developing technique, specifically the grip, stance and swing path. How do each of these relate to our tactical intention?</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>2</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Trading - backhands</td>
                                                <td>Developing backhand technique (as above)</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>3</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Movement</td>
                                                <td>Improving movement in a "back of the court situation" by looking out the split step/first step, footwork patterns, balance and recovery positions </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>4</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>First Serve and Return</td>
                                                <td>Developing technique to achieve greater control of direction and greater power. How can the returner neutralize an effective first serve?</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>5</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Second Serve and Return</td>
                                                <td>Developing technique to achieve greater consistency using a top spin or slice for control. How can the returner attack a second serve?</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>6</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Volleys and Smashes</td>
                                                <td>Developing technique to allow for more effective net play, both when in control of the point and when defending in the point.</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>7</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Building a Point</td>
                                                <td>How to gain the advantage over your opponent by controlling time and space? When to hit the ball cross court vs down the line, and when to approach the net</td>
                                            </tr>
