                                                <td>
                                                    <time datetime="2014-09-20" class="icon">
                                                        <em></em>
                                                        <strong>Week</strong>
                                                        <span>8</span>
                                                    </time>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>Neutralizing a Point</td>
                                                <td>How to get back in the point when under pressure by developing the skills to hit the ball on the run and neutralize effectively</td>
                                            </tr>
